<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>2</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Allow OBIEE to automatically assign colours to charts. The only exceptio=
n to this would be where there are small set of known fixed dimensional val=
ues, where it would be more consistent to fix the colours</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p></p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p><strong>3</strong></p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Where possible conditional formatting should stick to the three colours:=
 Red, Amber and Green. Where Red signifies a problem and Green signifies ac=
ceptable results</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p></p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
